Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰  我要是有什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.47,0:22:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知該如何面對封閉了內心的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也疏於努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還說這些做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快離開…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上  上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密爾諾夫上校？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校——！
